@startuml
title Login Activity Diagram

start
:1. Enter username and password;
:2. Authenticate credentials;

if (3. Credentials valid?) then (Yes)
  :4. Identify user role;
  :5. Grant system access;
else (No)
  :6. Display login error;
endif

stop

note right
Activity Description:
1. User provides login credentials.
2. System authenticates user.
3. Credential validation occurs.
4. User role is determined.
5. Access is granted.
6. Error message shown if invalid.
end note
@enduml